		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="738" y="287" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蟹沙皇进行左右双爪攻击2次，依次造成<span color="#7fbfff">80%,80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="511" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蟹沙皇依次喷出3枚「<span textDecoration="underline">岩居之种</span><span>」，种子落地造成</span><span color="#7fbfff">20%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="735" width="425" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蟹沙皇蓄力旋转而来，途经造成<span color="#b8b8b8">80%</span><span>伤害，且在路径上洒落3枚「岩居之种」。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="422" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放爆发之前，蟹沙皇引爆在场所有的「岩居之种」，每枚造成<span color="#7fbfff">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1183" width="441" height="172" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">蟹沙皇升空，开启<span textDecoration="underline">征服之界</span><span>，依次布下其下方内中外三圈，每圈各6枚种子的阵，30s后全部引爆。征服之界破溃后蟹沙皇陷入瘫痪，会消去所有种子，但会掉落3枚种子，</span><span color="#ffbfbf">本技能除瘫痪外产生的种子不会造成伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
