		<RichText x="66" y="1284" width="428" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">岩居之种：受到<span color="#99ff85">月/原/烈/超绽放伤害</span><span>后会转化，于1s后离地，对蟹沙皇造成等同于</span><span color="#ffdfbf">所受绽放伤害500%</span><span>的</span><span color="#99ff85">草元素</span><span>普通伤害。<br/>征服之界：需转化6枚岩居之种击落，瘫痪</span><span color="#ffdfbf">15s/5s(深渊)</span><span>。<br/>深渊特化下，蟹沙皇成功施放大招后</span><span color="#ffdfbf">全抗+70%</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
